Feeling&rdquo;, in Kathryn J. Norlock (ed.), <em>The Moral Psychology
of Forgiveness</em>, London: Rowman &amp; Littlefield, pp.
96&ndash;116.</li>

<li>Milam, Per-Erik, 2017, &ldquo;How is Self-Forgiveness
